PRE-ORDER ENDING SOON!GET MAX BOOST VOLUME 2 WHILE YOU CAN!YOU CHOOSE:  When you pre-order your books, you can select from Volume 1 or Volume 2 (either the Original or "Influencers and Friends" cover variant) or any combination therof! * To get your Name or Super Fan Square Printed in the book, you MUST fill out your order survey before the deadline. Details will be sent t you.  Date TBD.  MAX BOOST, VOLUME 2:  Filled with 167 pages, and Issues 40-98 which is the the second half of comics (Volume 1 was Issue 1-39) plus never-before-seen art in a gorgeous, collectible hardcover, exclusively ONLY AVAILABLE for pre-order HERE!  Max Boost is a story about Max and Otto, and their adventures in Motorville as they dream of one day becoming racing legends - but first, their stock civic needs more horsepower! :sad trombone:  And, before the dream of going PRO and have their names grace the Motorville Hall of Fame, they may want to be able to defeat their arch nemesis Todd in a quartermile drag race first.  In Volume 2, the story continues with Max and Otto in their stock pea-green civic, as they drag race at IDRC in a hopeless attempt to beat Todd’s V8. When all hope seems lost, Magically, a boost button appears on their dashboard- and of course they decide to push it… and the transformation begins. And from there, the story picks up quick - leading into more races, even more mayhem in Motorville. You’ll have fun meeting a new cast of characters, with new tuner cars, and some more high speed hijinks along the way.  Do you remember the Super Dupra?  The AWD Twins Zig and Zag?  BUT, the world of MAX BOOST is in danger.  Cars are starting to randomly disappear- and mysterious villains from a distant world are out to destroy MOTORVILLE.  The mystical Papa Wheely is the only one who knows the secret to saving Motorville, and why Max Boost has been chosen to become a unlikely hero.  This Volume 2 is full of surprises - and heck - we even have special guest appearances - like this dude you might recognize! So treat yourself to a great story, and a chance to own a rare collectible that is a part of original 90’s Tuner Culture!  And from there, close to 200 total pages of Max Boost have been published to date (Volume 1 and Volume 2 will be the complete story, up to date) about the misadventures  - from tuning upgrades, to police, drag racing, drifting, burnouts and torgue the story takes many twists and turns.Max Boost, Volume 2 is a joy ride for all car enthusiasts and comic book fans! Behind the Scenes and Additional Art Added to the Book!ALSO IN THE BOOK: BEHIND-THE-SCENES AND ART NEVER SHARED BEFORE! Max Boost Volume 1 has 100 Pages of the original comic, plus 50 pages of EXTRAS and never before seen art, original sketches, and more that is only available here on Indiegogo.  And exclusively for this campaign launch, you can get add-ons and exclusive Gifts never offered before (see below)! Max Boost - He is the underdog, and our unlikely hero.  Max is absolutely passionate about cars and racing, and will do anything it takes to find, build, and race the car of his dreams.  His number one enemy is Todd, and he is committed to bringing street-justice to Motorville by having Todd pay for all of the horrible things he does to those who have less horsepower than him.And, as the story develops, we find out what roles these characters play, as the very existence of Motorville may actually depend on this young group of street-rascals...    Otto - is Max's best friend and voice of reason.  Otto is basically the opposite of Max, as he is calm, collected, and is always thinking wisely.  However, he also knows it's almost impossible to stop Max when he has a "great idea", and knows it's better just get out of his way (and sometimes more entertaining!).  As a master tactician, Otto, has the skill of gently guiding Max along so he doesn't hurt himself... too much.  Todd -  Big V8, BIG Pistons, and even BIGGER EGO.  Todd is the town jock that you love to hate, and he makes it a "sport" to harass Max and Otto, and anyone else under 500 horsepower.  Maybe one day, Max and Otto will be able to teach him a lesson in humility, but they will need to find some horsepower and torque first!  Papa Wheely and his henchmen, Yin, Yan and Wok - He has the Horsepower and Torque!  Papa Wheely is the Proprietor of Papa Wheely's Performance Pagoda.  He's the one to see if you want you tuner car, tuned - but for a PRICE!AND, if you don't make your payments on time, you may end up meeting the his "Wu Tang Wack!"  Ese and 'Efe - The leaders of the Low Rider crew from Low Co., Ese and Efe' patrol the streets of Lotting Park - with 3 wheel motion, on chrome & white walls.  Don't get caught by them at the wrong time, in the wrong place, or you might find yourself getting "hit by switches".  Rip, Slug, Torch- Three mysterious bad dudes from a mysterious place have come to Motorville with suspicious motives.  Are they just looters? Or are the part of a bigger plan leading to the distruction of Motorville?  Let's find out...And, that's not all, there are many, many more characters in Max Boost for you to meet!  We WARNED YOU! -  We SOLD OUT of all collectible Volume 1 Exclusives in the first campaign, so now we're back with NEW items exclusively for Indiegogo SO GET THEM WHILE YOU CAN!!!! (Choose a reward level that includes these items, and follow those instructions)  NEW RUBBER KEY CHAINS - Brand new Exclusive Rubber Key Chains.  BRAND NEW LANYARDS (2 STYLES) - We love these lanyards!  You got Keys?  Well them you gotta get 'em! NEW STICKER SLAP PACK! - GET IT!!! Prototypes shown, designs may change! NEW COLLECTIBLE MYSTERY PIN SET - BRAND NEW SERIES 1 (the previous series was "SERIES 0"). This is a mystery set, and pins may be revealed throughout the campaign! :) BRAND NEW MAX BOOST GARAGE FLAG! - A huge printed flag (5 FT X  3 FT!) that you can hang in your garage next to your whip, at work, or in your room!  NEW BACKER CAR DECALS (2 STYLES) - +$10 for each decal, simply add to your pledge total.  Be loud and proud!LICENSE PLATE FRAME! - For your ride!  SECOND COVER "B" VARIANT - FRIENDS AND INFLUENCERS MASHUP!!! - And, for you collectors out there, we’re also adding a Second Cover Variant -  a suprise Max Boost MASHUP Cover which will have your favorite Influencers and my friends - ONLY available for this campaign! FRIENDS AND INFLUENCERS ON THIS SPECIAL EDITION COVER:
